data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bed, 2.5-bath residence boasts modern upgrades throughout. Enjoy the spacious living area with beautiful laminate floors and fireplace. The gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Step outside to a huge deck overlooking the pool. Upstairs, find a serene master suite with a private walkout balcony. With an attached garage and close proximity to amenities, this home offers luxury living at its finest!
